channel.title: Giving free help with setting up servers!
channel.description:
Helping people with setting up server for free, add me on skype taivo.grossberg1 . Also i can help people with 667 zenith sources. Ive notived that theres not so many good guides out there, so since im done with rsps's i could aswell help out people who are planning to make their own server (port forwarding, help with vps, errors, first server,explaining java etc.).
Dear Haters, I might be a noob but im atleast doing something for the rsps community.
